        <initializer>= true</initializer>
        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Usually, from several objects that fall into the peak, the closest one along the ray is selected. However, if exactPickFirst = true, then the object in which the pick exactly fell (for example, a point in point cloud) will be returned as the result, even if there are others within the radius, including closer objects. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
